title: Dark Endings
description: This book contains adult content 18+He's been gone for months. She doesn't know if he's alive. She's been aching for him.Willow has suffered, she's been doing the best she can without him. He saved her, he gave up his life for hers. The gang left her alone. She had nothing. Now they're back. They want to help. They're giving her hope. Can Willow get Jagger back before it's too late? Is she willing to risk her life for him? Is she willing to give it all up to save him?Come on this wild conclusion to the Dark Brother series, and fall in love all over again! Willow and Jagger will take you on a journey, in search of true love!
author: Bec Botefuhr
